properties.name: Canal Fulton, Ohio
properties.description: Posted by EmilylopezCanal Fulton OhioCanal Fulton is a town that was founded in the 1800\'s. The towns population is less than 5,000. Canal Fulton is known for its old buildings and haunted stories around the town. It is located in Northeast Ohio and is the most beautiful little town to visit.

properties.name: Eiffel Tower
properties.description: Posted by EmilylopezParisThe eiffel tower was built in 1889. people use the eiffel tower today for many different reasons it became part of the the french radio in 1918 and french television in 1957.

properties.name: Mauna Loa
properties.description: Posted by EmilylopezHawaiiMauna Loa is known to be the largest volcano in the world the estimated volume in the world is 9600 cubic miles. It takes up half of the state of Hawaii. Mauna Loa began around 1 million years ago.

properties.name: Mt.Everest
properties.description: Posted by EmilylopezLocationMt.Everest was founded 60 million years ago. It got its name from Sir George Everest in 1865 who was the first person to record the height and the location. The most danerous place on the mountain is khumba ice fall which has recorded 19 deaths. The climate on Mt.Everest changes dramatically as you move up the mountain. Many people have tried to overcome the harsh conditions but have failed.

properties.name: Sahara Desert
properties.description: Posted by EmilylopezLocationSahara Desert is the worlds largest desert. It stretches from the Red Sea to the Atlantic Ocean. Histoirians say that it dates all the way back to 3 million years ago. The saharah desert is home to many unusaul animals as well as unusaul plants.

properties.name: St.Agustine
properties.description: Posted by EmilylopezFloridaSt.Agustine is the nations oldest city. It is known as the "ancient city located between northeast and Central east Florida. St.Agustine is know for its unique shops and bed and breakfast inns.

properties.name: Statue of Liberty
properties.description: Posted by EmilylopezNew York CityThe Statue of Liberty National Monument celebrated her 100th birthday on October 28, 1986.The Statue was completed in France in July, 1884 and arrived in New York Harbor in June of 1885.

properties.name: The Alamo
properties.description: Posted by EmilylopezAlamo served as a home to missionaries and their indian converts. The Alamo was originally named Mission San antonio de Valero. In the early 1800\'s they referred to the old mission as the alamo a word known as cottonwood.

properties.name: University of Auburn Chapel
properties.description: Posted by Emilylopezauburn,alabamaThis chapel was built in 1851 by a presbyterian church. The chapel was used for a hospital for the wounded soliders during the Civil War.Whe the main building was burnt down at the college they also used the chapel for classrooms. Auburn University is known for its historic buildings. The chapel has had great effect on the people at attending the college.

properties.name: Youngstown Historical Center of Industry and Labor
properties.description: Posted by EmilylopezOhio Youngstown Historical Center was a center designed to teach people about the lives of Steel workers and what they went through everyday at work. This center holds pictures movies and tools. It gives a real life experience of what actually took place. It discusses the impact that the iron and steel industry had on Youngstown and there communities.
